1
00:00:00,344 --> 00:00:03,344
原创翻译：Smile4YourJeff
校订双语：dahongying

2
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:15,000
片名：《关键第四号》

3
00:04:58,097 --> 00:05:03,467
你知道 这样骑让你看起来很绝望
You know, showboating like that just makes you look desperate.

4
00:05:03,503 --> 00:05:07,269
是啊 “看看我 我还能反转一圈勒”真可笑
Yeah, "Look at me. I can flip my ski." Pathetic.

5
00:05:07,307 --> 00:05:10,401
- 是啊 - 丹尼尔 刚刚真棒！
- Yeah. - Daniel, that was awesome!

6
00:05:11,444 --> 00:05:13,708
妮可
Nicole.

7
00:05:17,483 --> 00:05:19,644
嘿 丹尼尔 妮可 走了吗？
Hey, Daniel, Nicole left, huh?

8
00:05:19,686 --> 00:05:22,814
你应该让我跟他讲讲话的
Should've let me talk to her.

9
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,800
妮可：去游泳如何？去5号码头见我

10
00:05:28,628 --> 00:05:30,493
哇哦！
Whoo-hoo!

11
00:05:37,603 --> 00:05:39,093
我真爱这个地方
I love it out here.

12
00:05:42,642 --> 00:05:46,078
北斗七星 是我的最爱
The Big Dipper. It's my favorite.

13
00:05:48,047 --> 00:05:49,742
- 你知道吗？ - 不知道
- Do you know that one? - No.

14
00:05:49,816 --> 00:05:52,546
我天文学才考了D (50～60分)
I got a D in Astronomy.

15
00:05:56,656 --> 00:05:59,557
我从来都没看过你跟其他人(女生)再一起
So, I never see you with anyone.

16
00:05:59,625 --> 00:06:03,026
还是你有女朋友吗？在外县市？
Do you have a girlfriend out of town or something?

17
00:06:10,002 --> 00:06:12,095
丹尼尔？ 丹尼尔？
Daniel? Daniel?

18
00:06:18,845 --> 00:06:22,042
我要让你察觉这个！
I want you to feel this!

19
00:06:23,383 --> 00:06:26,784
你接下来所要面对的
This is what's coming for you.

20
00:06:29,989 --> 00:06:31,115
丹尼尔 你还好吗？
Daniel, are you OK?

21
00:06:33,326 --> 00:06:34,918
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

22
00:06:39,732 --> 00:06:42,929
他是个怪物 他是个怪物…
He's a freak. He's some kind of freak.

23
00:07:28,714 --> 00:07:29,942
三号 已经死了
Number Three's dead.

24
00:07:31,517 --> 00:07:33,951
你还好吗？
You all right?

25
00:07:34,987 --> 00:07:37,820
- 还好 - 有其他人看到发生什么事吗？
- Yeah. - Anyone else see what happened?

26
00:08:18,464 --> 00:08:22,366
我已经告诉你不要带这个 这只会拖延我们的时间
I told you not to keep this crap. It just slows us down.

27
00:08:49,228 --> 00:08:50,957
好吧 我们出发
All right, let's go.

28
00:08:58,471 --> 00:08:59,938
丹尼尔
Daniel.

29
00:09:07,079 --> 00:09:10,879
这一部份就是我最讨厌的 搬家(逃避)…
This is the part I hate the most, the running.

30
00:09:10,917 --> 00:09:14,182
但它是唯一在我的生活里最真实的
But it's the only thing in my life that's real.

31
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:16,051
其余的 都不真实
The rest is a lie.

32
00:09:16,088 --> 00:09:18,283
即使是 亨利
Even Henri.

33
00:09:18,357 --> 00:09:20,257
大家都以为他是我父亲
People think he's my father.

34
00:09:20,293 --> 00:09:21,920
但他不是
He's not.

35
00:09:21,961 --> 00:09:26,523
他是从我们的星球派来的一位战士 指派来保护我的生命
He's a warrior from my planet, assigned to keep me alive.

36
00:09:27,833 --> 00:09:30,063
我不记得我的父亲
I don't remember my father.

37
00:09:30,102 --> 00:09:33,265
他所留给我的只有一个很奇怪的盒子
All he left for me was some kind of box.

38
00:09:33,306 --> 00:09:36,070
亨利说 当时机对的时候 他会把它(盒子)交给我
Henri says he'll pass it on to me when the time is right.

39
00:09:38,778 --> 00:09:41,872
我的第一个伤疤是在我9岁那年
I got my first scar when I was nine years old,

40
00:09:41,914 --> 00:09:44,439
靠近墨西哥边境
near the border of Mexico.

41
00:09:44,517 --> 00:09:47,281
让我从睡梦中惊醒
It woke me from my sleep.

42
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:51,347
这是第一个莫嘎多里安人发现我们在地球上信号
It was the first sign that the Mogadorians had found us here on Earth.

43
00:09:52,191 --> 00:09:55,126
我第二个伤疤是在12岁发生的
The second scar came when I was 12.

44
00:09:55,194 --> 00:09:58,493
在科罗拉多州 在场拼音考试中…
I was in Colorado, in the middle of a spelling bee.

45
00:09:59,465 --> 00:10:02,696
当我感受到… 我就知道二号死了…
As soon as I felt it, I knew Number Two was dead.

46
00:10:03,936 --> 00:10:06,700
昨晚 我得到了我的第三个疤
Last night, I got my third scar.

47
00:10:09,442 --> 00:10:14,311
莫嘎多里安人入侵我的星球时[洛林]那时我只是个小孩
I was just a kid when the Mogadorians invaded my planet, Lorien.

48
00:10:14,347 --> 00:10:16,815
我们9个小孩逃跑了
Nine of us children escaped.

49
00:10:16,882 --> 00:10:21,319
我们有天赋 当我长大后 要保护我们的人民
We were gifted, meant to protect our people when we grew up.

50
00:10:21,354 --> 00:10:25,051
但在还没有机会之前 大家都被杀了
We never got the chance. Everyone was killed.

51
00:10:26,292 --> 00:10:29,159
我们是星球中 最后的生存者
We are the last of our kind.

52
00:10:29,228 --> 00:10:33,460
但已经有3个人死亡了…
Three of us are gone. Dead.

53
00:10:33,499 --> 00:10:36,730
它们将一个接一个的把我们杀了
They are hunting us down, one by one, in order.

54
00:10:38,571 --> 00:10:40,334
我知道下一个就是我
I know I'm next.

55
00:10:42,108 --> 00:10:43,507
我是第四号
I am Number Four.

56
00:10:43,576 --> 00:10:44,873
好吧 所以…
All right, well, so...

57
00:10:44,944 --> 00:10:47,845
丹尼尔 其余的学期 不会在学校
Daniel won't be in school the rest of the semester.

58
00:10:47,913 --> 00:10:50,381
好的 你也是…
OK. You, too.

59
00:10:52,385 --> 00:10:53,750
你新的身分
Your new ID.

60
00:10:54,587 --> 00:10:59,024
还有这一次 避开麻烦 不要上课 不要组队 什么都不要…
And this time, you stay out of sight, huh? No school, no teams, nothing.

61
00:10:59,058 --> 00:11:01,049
约翰・史密斯 装得很像
John Smith. Very original.

62
00:11:01,127 --> 00:11:04,290
我不想装得很像 我希望能不被看见
I don't want to be original. I want to be invisible.

63
00:11:08,134 --> 00:11:10,295
这次不一样
This time was different.

64
00:11:10,336 --> 00:11:12,327
我不单只有一个伤疤
I didn't just get a scar.

65
00:11:12,371 --> 00:11:14,965
我 恩… 我看见三号
I, uh... I saw Number Three.

66
00:11:17,043 --> 00:11:20,706
我感觉的到刀 感觉的到他死 我们大家都可以感觉到
I felt the knife, I felt him die. I could tell we all did.

67
00:11:21,947 --> 00:11:25,314
- 其他人 - 我们要开始行动了
- The others. - We should get moving.

68
00:11:25,351 --> 00:11:28,013
莫嘎多里安人可能已经察觉你的气味
Mogadorians could've already picked up our scent.

69
00:11:29,321 --> 00:11:33,121
我们要去天堂 我那边有事情要处理…
We're going to Paradise. I have business to take care of.

70
00:12:41,827 --> 00:12:42,953
他是 伯尼・考萨尔
It's Bernie Kosar.

71
00:12:44,930 --> 00:12:46,397
玩美式足球的
Played football.

72
00:12:50,102 --> 00:12:54,266
- 是啊 他效力于克里夫兰 - 好的知道
- Yeah, he played for Cleveland. - Hm. Good to know.

73
00:12:54,306 --> 00:12:57,070
- 下次 让我来选地方 - 是啊
- Next time, I get to pick the place. - Yeah.

74
00:13:28,874 --> 00:13:31,536
全部在这… 我要去睡觉了…
That's all of it. I'm going to bed.

75
00:13:31,610 --> 00:13:35,205
喔 等一下… 我需要一张新照片…
Ooh. Hang on. I need a new picture.

76
00:13:36,515 --> 00:13:39,006
我们需要清空网路流传的东西
We have to wipe out anything that hits the Internet.

77
00:13:39,084 --> 00:13:42,383
说 “天堂”
Say "Paradise."

78
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:49,484
喔 该死
Oh, shit.

79
00:13:49,528 --> 00:13:51,723
这就是为什么我要把你消失为无形
This is why I need you to be invisible.

80
00:14:23,262 --> 00:14:24,286
回房子里
Get back inside.

81
00:14:26,232 --> 00:14:27,597
约翰
John.

82
00:14:27,666 --> 00:14:31,193
快 快进来里面
Come on. Come back inside.

83
00:14:40,746 --> 00:14:43,909
它是莫嘎多里安人也太小了吧 你不觉得吗？
Little small for a Mogadorian, don't you think?

84
00:14:46,285 --> 00:14:48,116
我确定它是别人养的狗
I'm sure he belongs to someone.

85
00:14:48,187 --> 00:14:51,281
它并没任何狗圈跟标志…
He doesn't have any collar or tags.

86
00:14:51,357 --> 00:14:53,917
你的主人在某个地方 一定很想你吗？
Hm. Somebody, somewhere, must miss you, huh?

87
00:14:56,929 --> 00:14:58,328
怎样…
Come on.

88
00:14:58,397 --> 00:15:01,093
多了一双眼睛 耳朵 帮忙顾家…
Another pair of eyes and ears watching the house?

89
00:15:01,834 --> 00:15:05,133
- 而且我也需要聊天的伴 - 跟我聊啊
- I'm gonna need somebody to talk to. - Talk to me.

90
00:15:07,539 --> 00:15:09,439
是啊 让你养吧
Yeah, keep the dog.

91
00:15:09,508 --> 00:15:10,907
要帮它取什么名子呢？
What are you gonna call him?

92
00:15:12,311 --> 00:15:15,246
取伯尼・考萨尔呢？
How about Bernie Kosar?

93
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:49,000
（天堂谷新闻：钢铁工人马尔科姆・斯贝尔曼仍然下落不明）

94
00:16:52,478 --> 00:16:54,207
你出来干嘛？
What are you doing up?

95
00:16:54,279 --> 00:16:55,871
我改变主意了
I changed my mind.

96
00:16:55,948 --> 00:16:57,779
什么东西？
About what?

97
00:16:57,850 --> 00:17:00,910
听着 在你左右真的很无聊
Look, uh, as much fun as you are to be around,

98
00:17:00,953 --> 00:17:04,013
我没办法当犯人 我一定要去上学
I can't be a prisoner. Uh, I have to go to school.

99
00:17:04,056 --> 00:17:06,081
- 不 不可能 太冒险了 - 拜托
- No. No way, too risky. - Come on.

100
00:17:06,158 --> 00:17:08,683
三号也是完全与外界脱离而Mogs干掉他了
Number Three was completely off the grid and the Mogs got him.

101
00:17:08,727 --> 00:17:10,251
- 但也保不住他 - 嗯啊
- Didn't save him. - Mm-mm.

102
00:17:10,329 --> 00:17:13,890
拜托 如果我融入团体 这样才会更安全
Come on. I'm gonna be safer if I blend in.

103
00:17:13,966 --> 00:17:15,433
我保证 我一定保持低调
I promise I'll keep a low profile.

104
00:17:15,501 --> 00:17:17,662
听着 即使我让你去 也很难行的通
Look. Even if I let you, and I'm not,

105
00:17:17,703 --> 00:17:19,933
你不可能就这样直接去学校上课而不被发现…
you can't just waltz into school and start class...

106
00:17:20,005 --> 00:17:22,599
你该不会以为你是唯一会伪造文件的人吧？
Do you think you're the only one who can forge documents?

107
00:17:23,876 --> 00:17:26,344
你有那个…？
Hm. Do you have a...?

108
00:17:26,378 --> 00:17:29,006
5天的粮食 换洗衣服 GPS 现金
Five days of rations, spare clothes, GPS, cash.

109
00:17:30,449 --> 00:17:31,711
- 你叫什么名子？ - 约翰・史密斯
- What's your name? - John Smith.

110
00:17:31,750 --> 00:17:33,274
- 你是哪里人？ - 多伦多
- Where are you from? - Toronto.

111
00:17:33,352 --> 00:17:35,252
你的皮肤看起来棕褐色的… 不像多伦多来的
You seem kind of tan for Toronto.

112
00:17:35,320 --> 00:17:39,484
圣菲 新墨西哥 我知道台词 好不好？
Santa Fe, New Mexico. I know the drill, OK?

113
00:17:43,929 --> 00:17:45,453
这个你留着 我每隔一个小时就会打电话给你
You keep this on you. I'll call you every hour.

114
00:17:45,531 --> 00:17:47,123
如果你不接 我就知道可能发生事情了
If you don't pick up, I know something's wrong.

115
00:17:47,199 --> 00:17:50,396
- 拜托 每个小时？ - 就是这样 不然你就请家教好了！
- Come on, every hour? - That, or you can home school.

116
00:17:50,436 --> 00:17:52,461
然后家教老师就是我
And I'll be your teacher.

117
00:17:53,605 --> 00:17:54,970
好啦
Fine.

118
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:58,942
嘿 约翰 不要像个白痴 保持低调点
Hey, John, don't be stupid. You keep your head down.

119
00:17:59,011 --> 00:18:00,387
我知道如何融入
I know how to blend in.

120
00:18:23,102 --> 00:18:24,467
好了 请坐
OK, doll. Take a seat.

121
00:18:24,503 --> 00:18:26,971
我帮你列印你的时间表 马上回来
I'll just print up your schedule. Back in a jiffy.

122
00:18:30,843 --> 00:18:32,470
我知道她是明星摄影师
I know she's the star photographer,

123
00:18:32,511 --> 00:18:34,411
但这样对其他学生不公平
but it's not fair to the other students.

124
00:18:34,446 --> 00:18:36,107
她把重要的耗材都要用光了…
She's using up all the vital supplies.

125
00:18:36,148 --> 00:18:39,982
埃默里 听着 “天堂里的陌生人” 至少她很有创意
Emory, come on. "Strangers in Paradise." At least she's creative.

126
00:18:40,052 --> 00:18:42,543
她的网站上的图片是完全不适当的
The pictures on her website are totally inappropriate.

127
00:18:42,621 --> 00:18:46,113
贝尔门先生 如果你想保留这些照片 你可以直说就好
Mr. Behrman, if you want to keep the photos, you should just say so.

128
00:18:46,158 --> 00:18:48,558
保留这些照片吗？他们已经传偏了网络了！
Keep the photos? They're already all over the Internet!

129
00:18:48,627 --> 00:18:51,994
你这样没经过别人的同意就上传到网络上是非常没礼貌的
It's a violation to post things like this without people's permission.

130
00:18:52,064 --> 00:18:53,361
你必须阻止…
You have to do something about this.

131
00:18:53,432 --> 00:18:55,866
贝尔曼先生 失陪几分钟 好吗？
Mr. Behrman, excuse us for a few minutes, OK?

132
00:19:03,442 --> 00:19:06,843
莎拉 这不像你
Sarah, this is not like you.

133
00:19:06,879 --> 00:19:09,313
是不是有什么事？
Is there something going on?

134
00:19:09,348 --> 00:19:12,249
- 一切都很好 - 莎拉？
- Everything's fine. - Sarah?

135
00:19:12,317 --> 00:19:15,309
- 真的啊 - 坐吧
- Honestly. - Have a seat.

136
00:19:16,188 --> 00:19:19,487
你不能让少数坏学生来影响你
You can't let a few negative students get you down.

137
00:19:19,525 --> 00:19:23,325
听着 我并不想看你孤零零的跟学校托解
Look, I don't want you to isolate yourself from the rest of the school.

138
00:19:23,362 --> 00:19:28,390
- 你应该享受这一年 - 好吧 我试试吧
- You should enjoy this year. - OK, I'll try.

139
00:19:28,467 --> 00:19:31,561
- 非常好 - 请把相机还回来？
- Good. - Can I please have my camera back?

140
00:19:31,637 --> 00:19:35,266
没有老师和学生的许可 不要再乱上传照片到你的网站 
No more photos on your website without teacher and student permission.

141
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:37,035
好的
OK.

142
00:19:37,109 --> 00:19:38,804
这里是你的时间表
Here's your schedule.

143
00:19:42,314 --> 00:19:46,045
主班为微积分学 B-WING第七间…
Homeroom is calculus. That's B-wing, room seven...

144
00:19:46,118 --> 00:19:51,886
哦 莎拉！你能不能带我们的朋友到他的内务柜？他是从圣达菲来的
Oh, Sarah! Could you show our friend to his locker? He's from Santa Fe.

145
00:19:51,924 --> 00:19:56,418
从明天起开始招聘 每个人都从明天起开始招聘
Job fair starts tomorrow. Everybody, job fair starts tomorrow.

146
00:19:56,495 --> 00:19:59,589
你用什么样的相机？
What kind of camera do you use?

147
00:20:00,499 --> 00:20:02,865
偷听？这样不会让你交到新朋友
Eavesdropping? That's not gonna win you friends.

148
00:20:02,901 --> 00:20:04,528
- 看那边 - 什么？
- Check it out. - What?

149
00:20:05,871 --> 00:20:08,704
那你帮我转告校长 办公室的隔音太差了
Tell that to the principal with a fish tank for an office.

150
00:20:09,408 --> 00:20:11,933
不听到也很难…
It's kind of hard not to hear.

151
00:20:13,245 --> 00:20:17,443
不好意识 其实学校隔音都很差
Sorry. This whole place is kind of a fish tank.

152
00:20:18,417 --> 00:20:20,908
嗯… 走廊走下去就是第7室了
Well... Room seven is down the hall,

153
00:20:20,953 --> 00:20:23,581
然后 呃 你的内务柜在那里
and, uh, that's your locker right there.

154
00:20:25,524 --> 00:20:28,652
祝你好运…嗯…
Good luck... um...

155
00:20:28,727 --> 00:20:30,524
哦 恩 约翰…
Oh, uh, John...

156
00:20:30,562 --> 00:20:32,655
…史密斯
...Smith.

157
00:20:34,433 --> 00:20:37,732
好的 你不想告诉我你的名字
OK. You don't want to tell me your name.

158
00:20:37,769 --> 00:20:38,793
没关系
That's fine.

159
00:20:45,711 --> 00:20:49,147
这真是我的名字 约翰・史密斯
That's really my name. John Smith.

160
00:20:58,390 --> 00:21:00,950
嘿 你好 您是新来的？
What's up, man? You new?

161
00:21:02,527 --> 00:21:06,827
马克詹姆斯 这是凯文、杰克逊、泰勒和马克斯
Mark James. This is Kevin, Jackson, Tyler and Max.

162
00:21:06,898 --> 00:21:08,627
- 嗨 你好吗？ - 约翰
- Hey, man, what's up? - John.

163
00:21:08,667 --> 00:21:10,635
很高兴认识你 约翰 你是哪里人？
Good to meet you, John. Where are you from?

164
00:21:10,669 --> 00:21:13,638
- 圣达菲 - 哦 新墨西哥
- Santa Fe. - Oh, New Mexico.

165
00:21:13,672 --> 00:21:15,003
在哪 都玩什么球类？
Play any ball out there?

166
00:21:15,073 --> 00:21:17,633
- 足球？ - 是啊
- Football? - Yeah.

167
00:21:17,676 --> 00:21:20,270
- 没有 - 都没玩吗？
- No. - Play anything?

168
00:21:20,312 --> 00:21:22,473
棒球？足球吗？乒乓球？
Baseball? Soccer? Ping-pong?

169
00:21:22,547 --> 00:21:24,981
没有
Nope.

170
00:21:25,017 --> 00:21:28,612
好的 不 没有关系 真的没关系
OK. No, that's cool, man. That's totally cool.

171
00:21:28,654 --> 00:21:30,622
多一个帮手也不错 对吧？
We could always use more boosters in the stands, right?

172
00:21:30,656 --> 00:21:34,956
听好 你如果需要什么 你要问我们 好吗？
Listen. You need anything, you ask us, OK?

173
00:21:34,993 --> 00:21:38,019
- 我们罩着你 - 我会记住的
- We got you. - I'll keep that in mind.

174
00:21:38,096 --> 00:21:42,590
聊天愉快 大家伙
Good talking to you, big guy.

175
00:21:43,268 --> 00:21:44,633
看看这是谁…？
Look who it is.

176
00:21:44,670 --> 00:21:46,865
小心点啊…！
Watch out, man.

177
00:21:46,938 --> 00:21:48,530
对不起 山姆
Sorry, Sam.

178
00:21:48,607 --> 00:21:52,543
废物！
Loser!

179
00:21:55,013 --> 00:21:56,207
等等我 白吃！
Wait up, fool.

180
00:21:56,281 --> 00:21:57,543
谢谢
Thanks.

181
00:21:59,318 --> 00:22:00,910
一定要爱第一流的…
Gotta love the classics.

182
00:22:00,986 --> 00:22:03,750
国王与校友… 科学的… 书呆子…
Homecoming king versus the science nerd.

183
00:22:05,324 --> 00:22:07,815
这样能让时间好过一点…
Just get better with time, don't they?

184
00:22:07,859 --> 00:22:11,351
- 那家伙 马克 他… - 不久就无关紧要了
- That guy, Mark, he's... - Soon to be irrelevant.

185
00:22:11,396 --> 00:22:13,887
今年是他的第三年 也是他人生中最威风的四年而已…
He's in the third year of the best four years of his life.

186
00:23:16,528 --> 00:23:20,624
所以 她很像“太阳能系统 太阳不围绕地球”
So, she was like, "The solar system's sun does not revolve around the Earth."

187
00:23:20,699 --> 00:23:22,633
""最好是啦""
I said, "Yeah, right."

188
00:23:25,570 --> 00:23:26,935
嘿 斯波克！
Hey, Spock!

189
00:23:27,005 --> 00:23:29,769
- 击中了吧！- 当心！飞碟 兄弟！
- Nailed it! - Heads up! UFO, brother!

190
00:23:29,808 --> 00:23:32,140
喔那一定很痛
That had to hurt.

191
00:23:32,210 --> 00:23:33,939
嘿 躺在那就好了啦
Hey, stay down, man. Just stay down.

192
00:23:34,012 --> 00:23:35,172
他要哭了 他要哭了…
He's gonna cry. He's gonna cry.

193
00:23:35,247 --> 00:23:37,715
- 哦 他妈妈来了耶…！ - 哦…
- Oh, Mommy's coming! - Oh...

194
00:23:40,051 --> 00:23:42,315
- 正击中脸耶 - 嘿 你没事吧？
- Right in the face. - Hey, are you OK?

195
00:23:42,387 --> 00:23:46,289
- 混蛋 - 哟 新来的！帮个忙？
- Assholes. - Yo, new dude! Little help?

196
00:23:56,134 --> 00:23:58,068
天啊！
Jesus!

197
00:23:58,103 --> 00:24:00,230
我没事！ 放开我…
I'm fine! Get off me.

198
00:24:00,305 --> 00:24:02,068
干嘛这样啊！
Come on, man!

199
00:24:02,107 --> 00:24:04,098
- 你还好吧？ - 不
- You OK? - No.

200
00:24:07,913 --> 00:24:10,507
你手臂的力量还真大
That's quite an arm you got there.

201
00:24:10,582 --> 00:24:13,415
是啊 天晓得？
Yeah. Who knew?

202
00:24:15,420 --> 00:24:17,786
那么 什么外星人的事情？
So, uh, what's with the UFO thing?

203
00:24:19,524 --> 00:24:20,889
我知道今天是你的第1天
I know it's your first day and all,

204
00:24:20,959 --> 00:24:23,553
但 早晚你都知道的
but, uh, sooner or later you'll figure it out.

205
00:24:24,629 --> 00:24:25,755
知道什么啊？
Figure what out?

206
00:24:26,932 --> 00:24:29,366
我绝对不配当你的朋友
I'm definitely not the guy you want to hang with.

207
00:25:25,156 --> 00:25:27,215
低调？
Invisible.

208
00:25:27,259 --> 00:25:29,227
我说的话你有记清楚吗？
You heard me when I said that, right?

209
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:15,000
第四号没有死在这儿

210
00:25:29,261 --> 00:25:33,357
是啊 因为如果我没记错的话 我不是在对空气讲话
Yeah. Yeah, because I remember you being there.

211
00:26:18,376 --> 00:26:22,278
让我们面对现实 不要有恐惧 我们时代的残酷
Let us face, without panic, the reality of our times.

212
00:26:22,314 --> 00:26:24,214
事实上 原子弹…
The fact that atom bombs

213
00:26:24,249 --> 00:26:28,447
也许某一天会掉在我们的城市 所以我们要随时准备好…
may, some day, be dropped on our cities. And let us prepare for survival

214
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:30,545
并了解武器对我们的威胁
by understanding the weapon that threatens us.

215
00:26:30,589 --> 00:26:31,613
是啊
Yeah.

216
00:26:37,862 --> 00:26:41,320
你适应得如何啊 兄弟？
How you settling in, bro?

217
00:26:42,567 --> 00:26:45,627
- 很好 谢谢 - 非常好
- Fine, thanks. - Good. That's good.

218
00:26:45,670 --> 00:26:49,037
我看你和史巴克成为了好朋友啊
I see you and Spock are vibing.

219
00:26:49,107 --> 00:26:51,041
没想到怪物也有感性的一面 是吧？
Got a bit of a soft spot for freaks, do you?

220
00:26:51,109 --> 00:26:52,838
谁在讲话？
Who's talking?

221
00:26:54,879 --> 00:26:57,848
哎呀
Yikes.

222
00:26:57,916 --> 00:27:01,909
听着 你是个可崇拜的年轻人
Look. It's cute, it really is. You are an adorable young man.

223
00:27:01,953 --> 00:27:04,148
但 这样刺激到我
But I find it irritating,

224
00:27:04,222 --> 00:27:06,349
所以保持低调 知道吗？
so keep it on the bleachers, OK?

225
00:27:06,424 --> 00:27:08,517
- 好 - 非常好
- All right. - Good. That's good.

226
00:27:08,593 --> 00:27:10,254
还有 有我在这的日子
Also, while I'm here,

227
00:27:10,295 --> 00:27:11,922
我给你一个建议
I'm gonna let you in on a little tip.

228
00:27:27,479 --> 00:27:31,210
找一个适合自己的地方 其余的就交给我 好吗？
Find your place fast. Catch the rest of this flick, OK?

229
00:27:31,282 --> 00:27:33,375
天啊 兄弟 你全身湿透了
Jesus, dude. You are soaking wet.

230
00:28:02,847 --> 00:28:04,906
约翰 起来吧 来吧 我们得走了
John, get up. Come on. We gotta go.

231
00:28:04,983 --> 00:28:06,007
约翰
John.

232
00:28:06,051 --> 00:28:08,576
- 约翰 - 我的手 什么…？
- John. - My hands. What...?

233
00:28:08,653 --> 00:28:10,917
- 亨利 我的手好痛！ - 约翰…
- Henri. My hands burn! - John...

234
00:28:10,989 --> 00:28:12,923
- 看着我放松 - 我到底发生什么事？
- Look at me and relax. - What's happening to me?

235
00:28:12,991 --> 00:28:14,549
这在家乡叫做遗传能力
They called them legacies back home.

236
00:28:14,626 --> 00:28:17,254
9人之中… 都有这样的能力…
You, the nine, you're the only ones who have them.

237
00:28:17,328 --> 00:28:18,659
- 遗传能力？ - 是得 没错
- Legacies? - That's right.

238
00:28:18,697 --> 00:28:20,722
你的父母是洛林派成员
Your parents were members of the Lorien Garde.

239
00:28:20,765 --> 00:28:23,256
你继承了他们的能力 天赋
You've inherited their abilities. Gifts.

240
00:28:23,334 --> 00:28:24,460
- 天赋？ - 是的
- Gifts? - That's right.

241
00:28:24,536 --> 00:28:26,333
我的手看起来像照明灯
My hands light up like road flares.

242
00:28:26,371 --> 00:28:28,931
- 你说这叫做天赋？ - 每个遗传者有自己的功能
- And you call that a gift? - Each legacy has its own function.

243
00:28:29,007 --> 00:28:31,032
接下来还会发生什么事？
There's... There's more coming?

244
00:28:31,076 --> 00:28:35,740
深呼吸 当你集中注意力 你会学会控制它们
As you breathe and focus, you're gonna learn to control them.

245
00:28:35,780 --> 00:28:39,682
- 好的 好的 - 就像这样…
- OK. OK. - Just like you're doing, right now.

246
00:28:39,718 --> 00:28:42,050
好吗？
OK?

247
00:28:43,254 --> 00:28:44,414
你觉得你的手怎么样？
How do your hands feel?

248
00:28:45,523 --> 00:28:49,584
- 比较好了 - 很好
- Better. - Good.

249
00:28:51,429 --> 00:28:52,953
那么现在要？
So, what now?

250
00:28:53,665 --> 00:28:55,155
现在？
Now?

251
00:28:55,233 --> 00:28:58,396
慢慢来 你会越来越强 越来越快
We wait. You're gonna keep growing stronger and faster.

252
00:28:58,436 --> 00:29:00,165
所以我需要你注意安全
I need you to be careful.

253
00:29:00,205 --> 00:29:03,299
现在 我需要你集中注意力 然后控助它
Right now, you have to focus your mind. Get some control.

254
00:29:03,374 --> 00:29:05,467
当然学会如何控制 才能再回去学校上课…
When you can do that, you can get back to school.

255
00:29:05,543 --> 00:29:08,137
我不希望引起怀疑 我在这还有事情没完成
I don't want to raise suspicion. I still have business here.

256
00:29:08,213 --> 00:29:10,044
在此期间 你的力量只会引起注意
In the meantime, your powers will only draw attention.

257
00:29:10,081 --> 00:29:12,413
随时注意自己 你明白吗？
You keep yourself in check, you understand?

258
00:29:12,450 --> 00:29:15,044
所以 我有这些能力 但却又不能使用它们…
So I got all these powers, but I'm not allowed to use them?

259
00:29:15,086 --> 00:29:16,280
没错
Exactly.

260
00:31:16,407 --> 00:31:19,638
还没到感恩节就买这些还真早啊…
A little early for Thanksgiving.

261
00:31:20,745 --> 00:31:22,269
纸 或 塑料？
Paper or plastic?

262
00:32:08,626 --> 00:32:09,752
要往这边…
And you wind it here...

263
00:32:29,580 --> 00:32:31,309
“天堂有陌生人”？
"Strangers in Paradise"?

264
00:32:33,885 --> 00:32:36,445
我知道 附庸风雅 自命不凡
I know. Arty, pretentious.

265
00:32:36,487 --> 00:32:38,682
嗯…这实际上并不是我想说的
Uh... That's not actually what I was gonna say.

266
00:32:38,756 --> 00:32:42,055
我的网站只是需要一个名字 所以就发现它
I just needed a name for my website and it was right there.

267
00:32:44,295 --> 00:32:48,129
他们应该把这个镇叫做“啼笑皆非”
You know, they should've called this town "Ironic."

268
00:32:48,166 --> 00:32:51,192
具有讽刺意味 俄亥俄州？
Ironic, Ohio? Has a ring to it.

269
00:32:53,905 --> 00:32:57,397
你怎么了？你看起来不一样 还是发生什么事
What's up with you? You look different, or something.

270
00:32:57,475 --> 00:32:59,340
莎拉 过来！我有一辆新自行车！
Sarah, come over! I got a new bike!

271
00:32:59,377 --> 00:33:02,005
好吧 下礼拜再去
OK, I will next week.

272
00:33:02,046 --> 00:33:04,378
- 帮我拿一下 - 好的
- Hold this for a second. - All right.

273
00:33:04,449 --> 00:33:06,508
喔 他们好可爱
Oh, they're so cute.

274
00:33:06,584 --> 00:33:08,677
呃… 我说实话
You know, uh... I mean it.

275
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:10,312
呃… 你的照片…
Uh... Your photographs...

276
00:33:10,355 --> 00:33:12,846
我父母叫我当保姆挣钱买胶卷
My parents make me babysit for film money,

277
00:33:12,924 --> 00:33:17,054
所以就找他们两个好了
and those are two of my victims.

278
00:33:17,128 --> 00:33:19,528
你知道 我 嗯…
You know, I'm, uh...

279
00:33:19,597 --> 00:33:22,998
实际上 我想夸夸你 但是 嗯…
I'm actually trying to pay you a compliment, but, uh...

280
00:33:23,034 --> 00:33:24,433
…但进行的不是很好
...it's not going so well.

281
00:33:25,536 --> 00:33:27,060
喔
Oh.

282
00:33:27,739 --> 00:33:30,037
好…嗯…
Right. Um...

283
00:33:32,176 --> 00:33:33,370
谢谢你
Thank you.

284
00:33:35,313 --> 00:33:38,714
我不知道 我只是感到 透过相机能看到真实的一面
I don't know, I just, um, see better through this thing.

285
00:33:41,085 --> 00:33:43,679
这就像是我自己个人学士探测器
It's like my own personal BS detector.

286
00:33:45,990 --> 00:33:47,218
来吧！让我们走吧！
Come on! Let's go!

287
00:33:49,293 --> 00:33:51,261
请问 你是不是忘了什么东西？
Excuse me. Did you forget something? 

288
00:33:51,261 --> 00:33:53,229
你有两件事情要做 你知道吗？
 You had two things to do, you know?

289
00:33:53,297 --> 00:33:55,458
- 锁门 关灯！ - 这就是山姆的爸爸吗？
- Lock the door and turn off the lights! - That's Sam's dad?

290
00:33:55,533 --> 00:33:56,591
他的继父
His stepdad.

291
00:33:56,667 --> 00:33:59,693
每天晚上都要我一直提醒你！
Every night it's the same thing with you!

292
00:34:05,009 --> 00:34:06,476
我到了
This is it.

293
00:34:15,086 --> 00:34:16,348
你住这边吗？
You live here?

294
00:34:17,588 --> 00:34:20,022
对啊 我在这长大的
Yeah, I grew up here.

295
00:34:24,462 --> 00:34:28,023
- 它只是普通的房子 - 我知道
- It's just a house. - I know.

296
00:34:33,738 --> 00:34:34,932
你饿了吗？
You hungry?

297
00:34:35,006 --> 00:34:38,305
那么 约翰几个星期前刚从圣达菲搬过来
So, John, just moved from Santa Fe a few weeks ago.

298
00:34:38,376 --> 00:34:39,968
- 史密斯 对不对？ - 嗯 是的 先生
- The Smiths, right? - Uh, yes, sir.

299
00:34:40,044 --> 00:34:43,104
- 你的父亲是一个作家？ - 是的 他是
- And your father's a writer? - Yes, he is.

300
00:34:43,147 --> 00:34:45,843
在这里 每个人都知道镇上的一切啊
Everybody really does know everything in this town.

301
00:34:45,917 --> 00:34:48,442
哦 八卦传播的像病毒一样快
Oh, gossip spreads like Ebola.

302
00:34:48,486 --> 00:34:49,783
问题的游戏！
Question game!

303
00:34:49,821 --> 00:34:52,119
哦！对不起 我的错
Oh! Sorry, my bad.

304
00:34:52,156 --> 00:34:54,283
- 好吧 大家把手机都放在篮子里 - 随你了
- All right, everybody, surrender them. - Here you go.

305
00:34:54,358 --> 00:34:57,657
所有的电子设备 来吧 莎拉谢谢
All electronic devices. Come on, Sarah. Thank you.

306
00:34:57,728 --> 00:34:58,854
交出来（亨利三次未接来电）
Hand them over.

307
00:34:58,930 --> 00:35:00,727
- 还有你 - 妈妈？
- And you. - Mom?

308
00:35:00,798 --> 00:35:03,733
晚餐后会还给他 晚餐后就会还给你
He'll get it back after dinner. You'll get it back after dinner.

309
00:35:03,768 --> 00:35:06,328
- 谢谢你 约翰 没事的啦！ - 好的
- Thank you, John. See? It's fine. - All right.

310
00:35:06,404 --> 00:35:10,738
圣达菲比较热闹 对不对？搬来这会很无聊吗？
So, Santa Fe's kind of hip, right? You bored silly here?

311
00:35:10,775 --> 00:35:13,437
不会啦 春季嘉年华要到了！
Nah, not with the spring carnival coming up!

312
00:35:13,478 --> 00:35:16,413
真的很有趣 你和你的家人一定要来
It's fun, and you and your folks should definitely come.

313
00:35:16,447 --> 00:35:18,745
哦 只有我跟我爸而已…
Oh, it's just me and my dad.

314
00:35:19,784 --> 00:35:20,808
那你妈呢？
Where's your mom?

315
00:35:20,852 --> 00:35:22,444
- 嗯… 我…  - 妈
- Uh... My... - Mom.

316
00:35:22,487 --> 00:35:26,981
没关系 我爸妈没有结婚…
No, it's fine. My dad and mom, uh, they didn't get married.

317
00:35:27,058 --> 00:35:29,959
嗯…好啦…你一定要去看看…
Uh, you know, check it out. Carnival.

318
00:35:29,994 --> 00:35:32,360
莎拉会在那拍很多照片…
Sarah will be there taking pictures for the paper.

319
00:35:32,430 --> 00:35:33,522
随意拍拍而已
Cheap labor.

320
00:35:33,598 --> 00:35:35,190
- 明明就很好 - 不
- That is not why. - No.

321
00:35:35,266 --> 00:35:38,030
- 她是一个非常有才华的摄影师 - 问题游戏！
- She's a very talented photographer. - Question game!

322
00:35:38,102 --> 00:35:41,162
好吧 小声点… 等等在玩…
OK. Keep your voice down, and we will play.

323
00:35:41,205 --> 00:35:44,902
我们吃饭很传统 而且 我们从来不会装得很客套
It's a dinner tradition. Otherwise, we'd never talk about the good stuff.

324
00:35:44,976 --> 00:35:46,341
是你听过最糟糕的吗？
Worst advice you ever got?

325
00:35:47,345 --> 00:35:48,642
看看这个…
"Pull this."

326
00:35:48,679 --> 00:35:49,907
拜托 停止！
Oh, stop!

327
00:35:49,981 --> 00:35:51,573
很恶心耶…
That's really gross.

328
00:35:51,649 --> 00:35:52,843
好啦…嗯…
OK, um...

329
00:35:52,884 --> 00:35:55,148
而且你父母也不会发现你偷跑出来…
"Your parents will never know you're gone."

330
00:35:55,186 --> 00:35:57,211
你爸妈也都不知道你偷跑去来… 所以她才会才这…
It worked with your folks. That's how she got here.

331
00:35:57,288 --> 00:35:58,778
- 拜托 停 - 我的天啊
- Stop it. Stop. - Oh, my God.

332
