00:53:28,138 --> 00:53:29,503
好的
OK.

513
00:53:36,346 --> 00:53:38,439
你的手好温暖
Your hand's really warm.

514
00:53:55,031 --> 00:53:56,965
我满脑子想的都是你…
All I think about is you.

515
00:53:57,033 --> 00:53:59,661
我也是一直想着你
All I think about is you, too.

516
00:54:23,593 --> 00:54:25,356
你到底从哪里来的？
Where did you come from?

517
00:54:27,897 --> 00:54:30,297
好了 妈 我知道了
All right, Mom! I got it!

518
00:54:38,908 --> 00:54:41,001
- 我… - 我该走了
- I, uh... - Yeah, I should go.

519
00:54:50,620 --> 00:54:51,598
再见
Bye.

520
00:55:29,000 --> 00:55:32,500
（山姆：我看见你在树林里的所为了
今晚我们需要谈谈 我住在阿尔丁街371号）

521
00:55:50,213 --> 00:55:53,341
约翰！在这
John! In here.

522
00:55:56,286 --> 00:55:57,913
那么 你到底是什么？
So, what are you?

523
00:56:00,457 --> 00:56:03,654
你把那些球员轻而易举的丢来丢去
You threw those football players around like it was nothing.

524
00:56:03,693 --> 00:56:07,561
而且你手上的东西 那不是人类会做的
And the hand thing? That's not human.

525
00:56:07,630 --> 00:56:10,929
所以我现在问你 你到底是什么？
So I'm asking you, what are you?

526
00:56:13,570 --> 00:56:15,128
你要我威胁你吗？
Do I need to threaten you?

527
00:56:15,205 --> 00:56:17,571
好吧 因为我用手机拍了下来
All right, 'cause I got some pictures on my phone,

528
00:56:17,640 --> 00:56:19,039
之后大家就会开始一直问我这些问题了
and they're gonna start some major questions.

529
00:56:19,075 --> 00:56:21,043
- 把它给我 - 不
- Give me that. - No.

530
00:56:21,077 --> 00:56:23,409
你知道我可以扁你的？
You know I can hurt you. Hm?

531
00:56:39,929 --> 00:56:42,159
留着自己看吧
Knock yourself out.

532
00:56:49,339 --> 00:56:52,365
我整个童年…
My entire childhood...

533
00:56:53,443 --> 00:56:55,070
…就像X-档案里的故事
...has been an episode of X- Files.

534
00:56:58,081 --> 00:57:00,572
你知道是什么滋味吗？
You know what it's like to feel something...

535
00:57:01,684 --> 00:57:04,448
这么强烈…
...so strong...

536
00:57:04,487 --> 00:57:06,421
…而且每天你都得告诉你自己
...that every day you have to keep telling yourself

537
00:57:06,456 --> 00:57:09,584
而相信你爸会带你离开这鬼地方
your dad's gonna come back and take you away from this shithole.

538
00:57:09,626 --> 00:57:12,322
而我所相信的是事实
And that everything we believed in was true.

539
00:57:12,395 --> 00:57:14,863
我并没有发疯
And that we were not crazy.

540
00:57:19,269 --> 00:57:20,293
拜托
Please.

541
00:57:25,708 --> 00:57:27,198
拜托
Please.

542
00:57:30,814 --> 00:57:32,145
你爸是对的
Your dad was right.

543
00:57:33,917 --> 00:57:35,145
什么？
What?

544
00:57:41,291 --> 00:57:42,849
我说他是对的
He was right.

545
00:57:45,195 --> 00:57:47,425
关于古代宇航员…
About ancient astronauts...

546
00:57:48,398 --> 00:57:50,958
其他星球的生物…
...life on other planets...

547
00:57:53,269 --> 00:57:54,566
所有的…
...all of it.

548
00:57:58,942 --> 00:58:02,469
是的 我… 我知道… 我知道他不会离开我们的
Yes! I knew... I knew he wouldn't just leave us!

549
00:58:02,512 --> 00:58:06,471
我是说 在墨西哥边境找到了他的车 但没见到人
I mean, they found his truck near the border of Mexico, and he was just gone.

550
00:58:06,516 --> 00:58:08,347
- 也许他们带走了他 - 山姆…
- Maybe they took him. - Sam...

551
00:58:08,418 --> 00:58:10,716
你知道的 如果他知道你在这里 他会回来的
If he knew you were here, he'd come home.

552
00:58:10,787 --> 00:58:14,120
- 你不能告诉任何人 - 不会 我才不
- You can't tell anyone. - No, I-I-I wouldn't.

553
00:58:14,157 --> 00:58:16,352
不 不 你必须答应我 不可以让任何人知道
No, no, no. You gotta promise me. Nobody knows this.

554
00:58:16,426 --> 00:58:20,556
在从我来的星球有人在找我
There are others from where I'm from looking for me.

555
00:58:20,630 --> 00:58:22,928
我在这很不安全…
I'm not safe.

556
00:58:22,999 --> 00:58:27,936
山姆！我知道你在那里 马上给我滚进来… 现在！
Sam! I know you are in there. Get your ass in the house, now!

557
00:58:29,038 --> 00:58:30,471
等我进去你在走…
Wait until I get inside and then go.

558
00:58:30,507 --> 00:58:32,236
山姆？
Sam?

559
00:58:34,244 --> 00:58:35,472
我答应你
I promise.

560
00:58:38,047 --> 00:58:40,743
太好了！
Yes!

561
00:58:43,820 --> 00:58:45,344
来吧
Come on.

562
00:58:59,836 --> 00:59:01,736
嘿 你这个疯子
Hey, you maniac.

563
00:59:01,804 --> 00:59:05,171
- 儿子？ - 到底怎么了…？
- Hello, son. - Hey, what's with the, uh...?

564
00:59:09,612 --> 00:59:10,601
你好 爸爸
Hello, Dad.

565
00:59:10,680 --> 00:59:12,739
詹姆斯警长说有些男孩昨晚受伤了
Sheriff James says some boys got hurt last night.

566
00:59:12,815 --> 00:59:14,874
他们几个昨晚在医院住院
Couple of them spent the night in the hospital.

567
00:59:14,918 --> 00:59:16,408
- 你说是4个吗？ - 是 4个
- You said it was four? - Yeah, four.

568
00:59:16,486 --> 00:59:19,512
- 美式足队的      - 是的
- On the football team. - Yeah, that's right.

569
00:59:19,556 --> 00:59:23,890
当然 他们什么也不说… 包括我儿子 马克
Of course, none of them are talking. That includes my own boy, Mark.

570
00:59:25,595 --> 00:59:29,725
- 你儿子是马克？ - 是的 我儿子
- Your son is Mark? - Yeah, that's right.

571
00:59:29,766 --> 00:59:31,791
你知道他打球的那只手受伤了
You know, that was his throwing arm that got hurt.

572
00:59:31,868 --> 00:59:33,859
他说当时你在场
He said you were there.

573
00:59:36,105 --> 00:59:38,596
嗯 不 我当时是跟一个女生在那
Uh, no. I was actually with a girl.

574
00:59:38,641 --> 00:59:42,737
所以我并没有很注意… 嗯…
So I wasn't paying any attention. Um...

575
00:59:42,779 --> 00:59:43,803
莎拉霍尔特？
Sarah Hart?

576
00:59:47,517 --> 00:59:52,079
没人想说到底真正发生了什么事…
Well, no one wants to be the first one to say what really happened.

577
00:59:52,121 --> 00:59:55,613
但 最后 会有人说的
But, eventually, someone will.

578
00:59:55,658 --> 00:59:58,354
我相信你是对的 谢谢你警长
I'm sure you're right. Thank you, Sheriff.

579
00:59:58,428 --> 01:00:00,794
如果有任何消息 我们会先告诉你的
If we hear anything, we'll let you know.

580
01:00:21,017 --> 01:00:23,679
- 他们有4人？ - 是的
- Four of them, huh? - Yeah.

581
01:00:25,288 --> 01:00:27,051
很困难吧？
Was it difficult?

582
01:00:27,924 --> 01:00:29,983
很简单
Piece of cake.

583
01:00:30,026 --> 01:00:32,654
很好 你开始掌握了
Good. Means you're getting it.

584
01:00:32,695 --> 01:00:34,720
上楼 收拾行李
Go upstairs, pack your stuff.

585
01:00:34,797 --> 01:00:36,162
就因为昨晚的事嘛？
Because of last night?

586
01:00:36,232 --> 01:00:38,826
因为我不喜欢有人一直来问问题
Because I don't like people showing up asking questions.

587
01:00:38,901 --> 01:00:41,927
- 我认为这将提高你的能量 - “他们在我们当中”
- And I think this is gonna raise a few. - "They walk among us."

588
01:00:41,971 --> 01:00:43,871
这是什么？ 更多怪异档案吗？
What is this? Some more "truth is out there" freaks?

589
01:00:43,940 --> 01:00:46,841
实际上 这是你
Except that's actually you.

590
01:00:46,909 --> 01:00:49,070
一定有人拍到你
One of the kids must have caught you on video.

591
01:00:49,145 --> 01:00:50,544
喔 该死
Oh, shit.

592
01:00:50,613 --> 01:00:52,672
他是个怪物
He's some kind of freak!

593
01:00:52,715 --> 01:00:54,012
我无法攻破防火墙
I can't get through the firewall.

594
01:00:54,050 --> 01:00:55,847
我们必须去那里 靠我们自己解决
We have to go there and take it down ourselves.

595
01:00:55,918 --> 01:00:58,045
他们(Mog)会看见这个 只是时间问题
Mogs see this, just a matter of time.

596
01:00:58,121 --> 01:01:00,419
打包行李 准备走了
Pack your stuff. We're leaving.

597
01:01:01,791 --> 01:01:03,554
我不走
I'm not going.

598
01:01:04,927 --> 01:01:06,724
我有听错吗？ 你说什么？
I'm sorry, what did you say?

599
01:01:07,830 --> 01:01:09,491
我说我不去
I'm not going.

600
01:01:09,532 --> 01:01:12,763
好 如果你想选下一个地方 给你选…
OK. If you want to pick the next place, that's fine...

601
01:01:12,835 --> 01:01:14,530
这从来不是我的战争！
It's not my fight and it never was!

602
01:01:14,604 --> 01:01:16,868
我也不记得有其他的星球
I can't even remember a world before this one.

603
01:01:16,939 --> 01:01:18,770
等等 等等…
Wait, wait...

604
01:01:18,841 --> 01:01:21,173
…是不是因为那个女孩？
...is this because of a girl?

605
01:01:23,012 --> 01:01:25,003
上楼 收拾你的行李
Go upstairs and get your stuff.

606
01:01:26,182 --> 01:01:29,379
- 你不是我的父亲 - 不 不 不 他已经死了
- You're not my father. - No, no, no. He's dead.

607
01:01:29,419 --> 01:01:32,252
他因为你而死 事实上 你知道吗？
He died for you. In fact, you know what?

608
01:01:32,321 --> 01:01:36,223
你根本不知道有多少人为此牺牲了而你才能活到现在！
You have no idea how many others have made sacrifices so you could live!

609
01:01:36,292 --> 01:01:37,782
牺牲不是为了让你可以在这里
And it wasn't so you could come here

610
01:01:37,860 --> 01:01:40,021
享受谈恋爱 跟正常男孩一样地生活！
and experience puppy love like a real live boy!

611
01:01:40,063 --> 01:01:41,758
我不走
I'm not leaving.

612
01:01:44,567 --> 01:01:47,434
约翰… 约翰！
John... John!

613
01:01:47,503 --> 01:01:48,765
我不走！
I'm not leaving!

614
01:01:50,039 --> 01:01:53,600
喔 是啊 我现在会这招了
Oh, yeah, I can do that now.

615
01:01:59,882 --> 01:02:01,042
嘿 约翰！
Hey, John!

616
01:02:12,028 --> 01:02:14,462
我要放开你了 好吗？
I'm letting go, OK?

617
01:02:15,598 --> 01:02:17,361
- 好吗？ - 好
- OK? - OK.

618
01:02:28,344 --> 01:02:31,438
- 在我们星球上… - 告诉我他们为何要杀我
- On our planet... - Just tell me why they want to kill me.

619
01:02:31,481 --> 01:02:35,975
Mogs他们不是殖民者 他们是屠杀者 他们继续前进
The Mogs, they don't colonize. They decimate. And then they move on.

620
01:02:36,052 --> 01:02:38,748
现在 他们来到了这里
And now, they've moved here.

621
01:02:38,788 --> 01:02:43,725
很少人能阻止他们 但你和其他五个可以
There are few forces that can stop them. You and the other five can.

622
01:02:43,760 --> 01:02:45,421
你的生存有重要的意义
You were saved for a bigger purpose.

623
01:02:45,461 --> 01:02:49,124
我不打算让你为了一个女孩儿而放弃
I'm not gonna let you throw that away for a girl.

624
01:02:49,165 --> 01:02:51,633
我不仅是为了女孩
She's not just a girl.

625
01:02:54,170 --> 01:02:56,297
我想过要离开她…
I think about leaving her...

626
01:02:56,939 --> 01:02:58,930
…但我办不到
...but I can't.

627
01:02:58,975 --> 01:03:01,409
我也不知道为什么
And I don't know why.

628
01:03:05,381 --> 01:03:09,283
我们不能爱上人类 更不能永远和我们在一起
We don't love like the humans. With us, it's forever.

629
01:03:13,389 --> 01:03:15,220
你要记在心里
You never forget.

630
01:03:17,727 --> 01:03:22,164
如果她是为了你 那就别让他们赢
If she is that for you, then don't let them win.

631
01:03:22,198 --> 01:03:24,564
切记自己的身份
Or you'll never forgive yourself.

632
01:03:27,670 --> 01:03:28,694
我们必须走了
Now, we have to go.

633
01:03:30,006 --> 01:03:32,668
我今晚会注意网络的 你只有1天时间
I'll take care of the website tonight. Buy you a day.

634
01:03:32,742 --> 01:03:36,576
1天？ 告别吗？
A day? To say goodbye?

635
01:03:36,646 --> 01:03:38,876
比起其他人算多的了
That's more than the rest of us had.

636
01:03:57,366 --> 01:03:59,266
他是个怪物啊！
He's some kind of freak!

637
01:04:09,879 --> 01:04:12,575
亨利 我去找莎拉了
Henri, I'm going to Sarah's.

638
01:04:16,519 --> 01:04:17,543
亨利？
Henri?

639
01:04:38,841 --> 01:04:41,605
亨利？喂？亨利？
Henri? Hello? Henri?

640
01:04:41,677 --> 01:04:46,307
我不是 过来我会告诉你怎么找到他
No, but come here and I'll tell you how to find him.

641
01:04:46,382 --> 01:04:48,179
你是谁？亨利在哪里？
Who are you? Where's Henri?

642
01:04:48,217 --> 01:04:51,118
华沙 印第安纳州威拉德417号
417 Willard Court, Warsaw, Indiana.

643
01:05:01,931 --> 01:05:04,229
快点 接电话呀
Come on, come on.

644
01:05:04,267 --> 01:05:05,791
我需要你帮忙
I need your help.

645
01:05:10,973 --> 01:05:12,804
所以那些家伙… 那些家伙 别…？
So, you guys... you guys don't...

646
01:05:12,875 --> 01:05:15,207
- 是绑架吗？ - 是
- Abduct people? - Yeah.

647
01:05:15,244 --> 01:05:16,268
不是
No.

648
01:05:16,312 --> 01:05:19,770
是别的家伙 正在追捕你的那伙？
But the other guys, the ones that are chasing you...

649
01:05:19,849 --> 01:05:21,009
他们会绑架吗？
...they do?

650
01:05:42,405 --> 01:05:43,895
是…
That's it.

651
01:05:45,775 --> 01:05:47,106
谢谢
Thanks.

652
01:05:54,884 --> 01:05:57,375
哇 你带了把枪？
Whoa! You brought a gun?

653
01:05:57,453 --> 01:06:00,445
是的 我从爱德那偷的 会派上用场的 来吧
I stole it from Ed. It might come in handy. Let's go.

654
01:06:00,523 --> 01:06:03,856
- 不 - 老兄 我来是帮你的
- No. - Dude, I came here to help you.

655
01:06:03,926 --> 01:06:07,453
你帮过了 现在回家吧
You have. Now, go home.

656
01:06:25,715 --> 01:06:27,376
哇！
Whoa!

657
01:06:30,119 --> 01:06:32,178
- 你在干嘛？ - 我是不会走的
- What are you doing? - I'm not bailing.

658
01:06:32,254 --> 01:06:33,983
万一那些也是抓我爸爸的人呢？
What if these Mog people took my dad?

659
01:07:06,022 --> 01:07:10,459
真神了！
Holy shit!

660
01:07:10,526 --> 01:07:12,687
你是怎么办到的？
But you just dead-bolted it.

661
01:07:14,196 --> 01:07:16,892
- 好了 得计划一下 - 是啊
- OK. New plan. - Yeah.

662
01:07:16,966 --> 01:07:20,060
跟着那家伙他回来时发信号给我好吗？
You follow that guy and you text me if he comes back, OK?

663
01:07:20,102 --> 01:07:21,933
好的 我这就去
Copy that. I'm on it.

664
01:08:56,165 --> 01:08:57,189
亨利
Henri.

665
01:09:11,647 --> 01:09:13,444
- 你没事吧？ - 你不应该来这里
- Are you OK? - You're not supposed to be here.

666
01:09:13,482 --> 01:09:15,643
- 怎么了？ - Mogs设了一个陷阱
- What happened? - The Mogs set this up.

667
01:09:15,684 --> 01:09:18,517
我们得离开 他们要来了
We need to leave. They're coming.

668
01:09:18,554 --> 01:09:21,523
你们都不要动 否者我会杀了这孩子
Everybody stays right where they are or I'll shoot this kid.

669
01:09:21,557 --> 01:09:24,151
说到做到 举起手来
I'll do it! Get your hands up!

670
01:09:24,193 --> 01:09:25,490
很高兴枪派上用场了
So glad you brought the gun.

671
01:09:26,862 --> 01:09:28,193
马尔科姆的儿子
You're Malcolm's boy.

672
01:09:29,532 --> 01:09:32,797
- 关掉电灯 好吗？ - 闭嘴！举起手来！
- Get the lights, will you? - Shut up! Get your hands up!

673
01:09:38,674 --> 01:09:39,698
噢！
Oh!

674
01:09:44,847 --> 01:09:48,374
你就是视频网站上的那个
You! You're the one from the video on our site.

675
01:09:48,450 --> 01:09:51,510
- 他们要找的人 - 他们要找谁？
- The one they're after. - The one who's after?

676
01:09:51,554 --> 01:09:54,352
- 他在说什么？ - Mogs 他们已经在这里…
- What's he talking about? - The Mogs, they've been here.

677
01:09:54,390 --> 01:09:55,721
- 这是圈套 - 是啊
- This was a trap. - Yeah.

678
01:09:55,791 --> 01:09:57,509
拜托 老兄 不管他们是什么
These dudes, whatever they are, man,

679
01:09:57,509 --> 01:09:59,227
他们有计划 你知道我在说什么吗？
they got plans, know what I'm sayin'?

680
01:09:59,261 --> 01:10:01,559
- 约翰… - 我是说 我是那家伙 我就是出阴谋的人
- John... - I'm that guy, the conspiracy guy.

681
01:10:01,597 --> 01:10:04,532
没人会给我说废话的机会 但这是真的 伙计
Nobody gives a crap what I say. But this is real, man!

682
01:10:04,567 --> 01:10:05,966
约翰 该走了
John. It's time to leave.

683
01:10:06,035 --> 01:10:09,732
他们喜欢地球 他们会接管整改地球 和一切事物
They like it here, Earth. They're gonna take all this shit, everything!

684
01:10:09,805 --> 01:10:11,102
约翰 现在
John! Now!

685
01:10:11,173 --> 01:10:13,198
我们得按他们说的做 否则我们都得死
