- Who is this tool? - Sam, focus.

867
01:28:23,097 --> 01:28:25,657
是什么冲出了汽车？
What flew out of the truck?

868
01:28:29,771 --> 01:28:32,331
来吧 走 走
Come on! Go, go!

869
01:28:32,373 --> 01:28:35,672
山姆 快点 走
Sam. Come on! Go!

870
01:28:39,947 --> 01:28:41,710
来吧 快点
Come on! Come on!

871
01:28:44,819 --> 01:28:47,151
快啊！
Come on!

872
01:29:55,923 --> 01:29:58,255
- 打我 - 什么？
- Hit me. - What?

873
01:29:58,326 --> 01:30:00,726
你的光线 我需要加电
With your lumen. I need to power-up.

874
01:30:02,930 --> 01:30:04,295
打我！
Hit me!

875
01:30:15,276 --> 01:30:17,107
红牛攻击娘娘腔
Red Bull's for pussies.

876
01:30:19,447 --> 01:30:21,574
他杀了亨利 我对付他
He killed Henri. I want him.

877
01:30:58,152 --> 01:30:59,551
四
Four!

878
01:31:11,766 --> 01:31:13,859
你擅长于用双手
You're good with your hands.

879
01:31:13,935 --> 01:31:15,903
- 谢谢 - 没问题
- Thanks. - No problem.

880
01:31:17,405 --> 01:31:21,705
- 我的狗 他… 他只是… - 是啊 她是合成兽
- My dog, he, uh... he just... - Yeah, he's a chimera.

881
01:31:21,776 --> 01:31:23,903
他在洛林就和我在一起
He came with you from Lorien.

882
01:31:23,978 --> 01:31:26,378
有些人不得不找到你
Someone had to look after you.

883
01:32:29,477 --> 01:32:31,570
你又带着枪 你是当真的吗
You brought a gun? Are you serious?

884
01:32:31,612 --> 01:32:34,046
- 什么？ 也许能用得着 - 走这边
- What? It might come in handy. - This way.

885
01:32:44,759 --> 01:32:45,783
走！
Go!

886
01:32:54,769 --> 01:32:56,396
- 带着她穿过隧道 - 明白！来吧！
- Take her back to the tunnel! - Got it! Come on!

887
01:33:03,744 --> 01:33:05,974
真是…！
Holy...!

888
01:33:10,585 --> 01:33:11,882
我玩了很多Xbox游戏
I play a lot of Xbox.

889
01:34:51,485 --> 01:34:55,751
4号 我觉得你有我需要的某些东西
Number Four, I think you have something I need. Hm?

890
01:34:57,358 --> 01:35:01,727
哦 谢谢你对我真很好啊
Oh, thank you for making this so nice and easy.

891
01:35:01,762 --> 01:35:07,029
一想到很快就会终结来自剩余你们星球的人了 这太好了
Think of how quickly we'll finish off the rest of the planet. It's fantastic!

892
01:35:07,768 --> 01:35:10,396
很快 我会终结你们全部
Soon, I'll be done with all of you.

893
01:35:10,438 --> 01:35:12,702
放轻松
Just relax.

894
01:35:14,108 --> 01:35:17,874
你无法阻止所有发生的一切 永远不可能
You can't stop what's coming. You never could.

895
01:35:17,912 --> 01:35:20,005
你…
You have...

896
01:35:20,047 --> 01:35:22,481
…不知道…
...no idea...

897
01:35:23,684 --> 01:35:25,151
…我擅长的地方
...what I'm capable of.

898
01:36:39,627 --> 01:36:40,821
约翰
John.

899
01:36:44,098 --> 01:36:45,793
能阻挡火吗？
Fireproof?

900
01:36:46,967 --> 01:36:49,333
我不是叫你待在哪？
I told you to stay tuned.

901
01:37:18,232 --> 01:37:20,359
好了 给我 来吧
All right, give me that. Come on.

902
01:37:21,235 --> 01:37:22,463
谢谢你
Thank you.

903
01:37:53,500 --> 01:37:57,493
太扫兴了 那就没有跟踪器了？
Oh. Well, that was disappointing. So, not a tracking device?

904
01:37:57,538 --> 01:37:59,597
不 这就是
No, it was.

905
01:37:59,673 --> 01:38:02,073
- 你也感觉到了？ - 是啊
- Did you feel that, too? - Yeah.

906
01:38:02,142 --> 01:38:05,305
- 我们知道需要去哪里 - 是的 我们能找到其他人的
- We know where we need to go. - Yeah, we can find the others.

907
01:38:11,552 --> 01:38:14,749
- 这 - 谢谢你
- Here. - Thank you.

908
01:38:15,723 --> 01:38:17,588
我希望这不会给你带来什么麻烦
I hope this doesn't get you in trouble.

909
01:38:17,625 --> 01:38:22,119
会 证据会随着时间而丢失的
Nah. Stuff goes missing from evidence all the time.

910
01:38:22,196 --> 01:38:24,596
我爸爸不会知道的
My dad won't even know.

911
01:38:24,632 --> 01:38:27,533
- 你现在必须往西行走 - 为什么？
- You want to be heading west now. - Why?

912
01:38:27,568 --> 01:38:30,059
因为我告诉我爸爸你去了东边
Because I told my dad you're going east.

913
01:38:37,978 --> 01:38:41,880
- 6号 山姆能我们一起走吧 - 什么？
- Six, Sam's coming with us. - What?

914
01:38:42,983 --> 01:38:44,746
- 没门 - 他现在也是我们的成员
- No way. - He's one of us now.

915
01:38:44,785 --> 01:38:47,015
我们必须找到他的父亲
We need to find his father.

916
01:38:50,624 --> 01:38:54,025
你拖累我们的话 我会亲手干掉你
You slow us down, I'll shoot you myself.

917
01:38:54,094 --> 01:38:56,562
我相信你 能走了吧？
And I believe you. Could we go now?

918
01:39:02,536 --> 01:39:04,663
保持稳定
Stay tuned.

919
01:39:04,738 --> 01:39:07,502
- 更安全 - 是的
- Safer. - Yeah.

920
01:39:07,574 --> 01:39:09,132
我知道
I know.

921
01:39:10,344 --> 01:39:12,812
关于亨利的事我很抱歉
Really sorry about what happened with Henri.

922
01:39:14,081 --> 01:39:15,844
我也是
Me, too.

923
01:39:19,219 --> 01:39:21,710
你知道的 我会再找到你的
You know I'll find you again.

924
01:39:24,024 --> 01:39:27,016
可能吧 我还会在这的
Probably still be here.

925
01:39:28,228 --> 01:39:29,820
这地方很迷人
It's the people that make the place.

926
01:39:30,597 --> 01:39:32,929
- 对吧？ - 是啊
- Right? - Yeah.

927
01:39:39,273 --> 01:39:43,141
亨利警告我 我们只能爱一个人
Henri warned me that we only fall for one person.

928
01:39:45,346 --> 01:39:46,813
永远？
Ever?

929
01:39:47,648 --> 01:39:49,081
永远
Ever.

930
01:41:21,875 --> 01:41:24,776
这是我第一个没有亨利陪伴而离开的城镇
This is the first town I've left without Henri.

931
01:41:25,712 --> 01:41:29,170
但同样也是第一个我有理由回来的城镇
But it's also the first one I have a reason to come back to.

932
01:41:30,551 --> 01:41:34,043
亨利是对的 我们变得更强大了
Henri was right, we're stronger together.

933
01:41:34,588 --> 01:41:37,182
所以我们会找到其他人
So we will find the others.

934
01:41:39,426 --> 01:41:44,056
我的星球叫做洛瑞恩 但地球现在是我们的家园
My planet is called Lorien, but Earth is my home now.

935
01:41:45,099 --> 01:41:48,796
她是全宇宙最美丽的地方
It's as good a place as any in the universe.

936
01:41:48,836 --> 01:41:51,270
而且永远都会保持这样
And that's how it's going to stay.

